{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/thibauts/rescale-vertices\">rescale-vertices</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<h3 id=\"rescales-vertices-to-the-dimensions-of-a-target-bounding-box\">Rescales vertices to the dimensions of a target bounding box</h3>\n<p>Accepts bounding boxes and positions of arbitrary dimensions.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\">Install</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source shell\"><span>$&#xA0;npm&#xA0;install&#xA0;rescale-vertices</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;rescaleVertices&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;rescale-vertices&apos;);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;positions&#xA0;=&#xA0;[&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[-1,&#xA0;&#xA0;0,&#xA0;&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;1,&#xA0;&#xA0;0,&#xA0;-1],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;0,&#xA0;-1,&#xA0;&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;0,&#xA0;&#xA0;1,&#xA0;&#xA0;1]&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>];</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;targetBounds&#xA0;=&#xA0;[</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[-1,&#xA0;-2,&#xA0;-3],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;1,&#xA0;&#xA0;2,&#xA0;&#xA0;3]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>];</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;Takes&#xA0;the&#xA0;source&#xA0;bounding-box&#xA0;as&#xA0;an&#xA0;optional&#xA0;3rd&#xA0;parameter.&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;If&#xA0;not&#xA0;provided&#xA0;the&#xA0;bounding-box&#xA0;is&#xA0;computed&#xA0;internally.</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;positions&#xA0;=&#xA0;rescaleVertices(positions,&#xA0;targetBounds&#xA0;/*,&#xA0;sourceBounds&#xA0;*/);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>console.log(positions);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>/*</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>[&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;-1,&#xA0;&#xA0;0,&#xA0;&#xA0;0&#xA0;],&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;&#xA0;1,&#xA0;&#xA0;0,&#xA0;-3&#xA0;],&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;&#xA0;0,&#xA0;-2,&#xA0;&#xA0;0&#xA0;],&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;[&#xA0;&#xA0;0,&#xA0;&#xA0;2,&#xA0;&#xA0;3&#xA0;]&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>*/</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n"}